reviewText:
I liked the price... and love this series.  I still need Series 14, 16 & 17.  Can't find affordable
prices for them though.  I just wish I could find where I could watch this Series since there is
no good prices avail.now.
We just need to have someone have season 16 available for us.

There is no graphic sex or violence by today's standards. It's set in a small Yorkshire village and the people get into as many scrapes and scandals etc. as in the real world. Each of the characters can make you laugh or cry but if nothing else pleases you the '60's and '70's music is great.
